1234 class Google_DriveService extends Google_Service {
1235  public $about;
1236  public $apps;
1237  public $changes;
1238  public $channels;
1239  public $children;
1240  public $comments;
1241  public $files;
1242  public $parents;
1243  public $permissions;
1244  public $properties;
1245  public $realtime;
1246  public $replies;
1247  public $revisions;
1253  public function __construct(Google_Client $client) {
1254  $this->servicePath = 'drive/v2/';
1255  $this->version = 'v2';
1256  $this->serviceName = 'drive';
